## Boolean operators

```julia
# Boolean operators
!true   # => false
!false  # => true
1 == 1  # => true
2 == 1  # => false
1 != 1  # => false
2 != 1  # => true
1 < 10  # => true
1 > 10  # => false
2 <= 2  # => true
2 >= 2  # => true
# Comparisons can be chained
1 < 2 < 3  # => true
2 < 3 < 2  # => false
```

